F

File - Class in fplogn
Aproach for making a File, every File knows in which Folder it is located, and it's name, also includes the size of the file and the user it belongs to.
File(String, Folder, long, String) - Constructor for class fplogn.File
Builds a new File with the characteristics.
FileStructure - Class in fplogn
FileStructure class allows the user to insert Files and search them by name, size, extension, user and parent Folder with a O(log(n)) complexity.
FileStructure() - Constructor for class fplogn.FileStructure
Builds a new FileStructure.
Folder - Class in fplogn
Folder class is just a File which is used to make the file's paths, then it's children Files have a reference to its parent Folder. essentially it's just like any other File, except that for being a parent of any File, it has to be a Folder.
Folder(String, Folder, String) - Constructor for class fplogn.Folder
Builds a new Folder with the given characteristics and inside the given Folder.
Folder(String, Folder, long, String) - Constructor for class fplogn.Folder
Builds a new Folder with the given characteristics and inside the given Folder. also includes the option to add the size of the new folder
